---
title: CSS Bar Chart
description: Animated bar chart using CSS custom properties for heights and `@keyframes` grow animation.
slug: bar-chart
cssFile: bar-chart.css
explanation: "Each bar uses `height: var(--h)` where `--h` is set inline (e.g. `style=\"--h:65%\"`). The `@keyframes` animation uses `scaleY` from 0 to 1 with `transform-origin: bottom` so bars grow upward. Staggered `animation-delay` values from `nth-child` selectors make bars appear sequentially. The container's `align-items: flex-end` anchors bars to the bottom baseline. `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` gives an elastic pop."
---
{% extends "example.njk" %}
{% block demo %}
<div class="chart-area">
	<p class="chart-title">Weekly visitors</p>
	<div class="bar-chart">
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">65</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 65%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Mon</span>
		</div>
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">45</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 45%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Tue</span>
		</div>
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">80</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 80%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Wed</span>
		</div>
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">55</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 55%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Thu</span>
		</div>
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">90</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 90%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Fri</span>
		</div>
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">70</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 70%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Sat</span>
		</div>
		<div class="bar-col">
			<span class="bar-val">30</span>
			<div class="bar" style="--h: 30%"></div>
			<span class="bar-label">Sun</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block html_code %}
{%- highlight "html" %}
<div class="bar-chart">
  <div class="bar-col">
    <div class="bar" style="--h: 65%"></div>
    <span class="bar-label">Mon</span>
  </div>
  <!-- more columns -->
</div>
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}

{% block css_code %}
{%- highlight "css" %}
.bar {
  height: var(--h);
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
  animation: bar-grow .8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) both;
}

@keyframes bar-grow {
  from {
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: bottom;
  }
}
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}
